mystuff
=======
	my personal OpenBSD ports

notes
-----
	* create /etc/mk.conf with the following options:
		- SUDO=doas
		- PORTS_PRIVSEP=yes 
	* create or add to /etc/doas.conf the following options:
		- permit keepenv nopass josegpt as _pbuild
		- permit keepenv nopass josegpt as _pfetch
	* clone ports under /usr
	* go to /usr/ports and run:
		- doas make fix-permissions
    * add users to the end of /usr/ports/infrastructure/db/user.list
        - 2000  _josegptcom    _josegptcom    www/josegptcom
